### 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

# 响应示例:
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "success",
#   "data": {
#     "id": 1,
#     "username": "testuser",
#     "nickname": "测试用户",
#     ...
#   }
# }

### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

# 响应示例:
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "success",
#   "data": {
#     "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...",
#     "user": { ... }
#   }
# }

### 获取个人资料（替换 token）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查询省级地区
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/regions?level=2

### 查询某城市的景点（替换 regionId）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/attractions?regionId=1&sortBy=likes

### 查询景点详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/attractions/1

### 单文件上传（替换 token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="travel.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# 响应示例:
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "success",
#   "data": "/uploads/2026/06/13/a1b2c3d4.jpg"
# }

### 多文件上传（替换 token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/file/upload/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./photo1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./photo2.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--
